Package commander

This package contains classes dealing with controlling the file tagging system.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Class Description
CommandManager This class is responsible for holding system commands, whether self-invoked or indirectly-invoked by the user (through UI).
 

Enum Summary
Enum Description
CommandManager.CmdCodes Codes for tagging system commands - used as keys to get concrete command objects through the getCommand method.
 

Package commander Description

This package contains classes dealing with controlling the file tagging system. It enables the control of each subsystem - the backbone of the system in some way.
